        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Supporting Trucking Efficiency and Emission Reductions Act or the STEER Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to establish a voucher program for expenses associated with retrofitting certain heavy-duty trucks with emission-reducing technologies.</p>]]>
        </text>
